===珀迪-欧文甲基化法===
[[File:Purdie_methylation.png|500px]]

珀迪-欧文甲基化法是采用[[糖类|糖类]]与过量[[碘甲烷|碘甲烷]]在[[氧化银|氧化银]]存在的条件下发生[[彻底甲基化反应|彻底甲基化反应]]的一种特定甲基化方法。<ref name="Purdie Irvine 1903 pp. 1021–1037">{{cite journal | last=Purdie | first=Thomas | last2=Irvine | first2=James C. | title=C.—The alkylation of sugars | journal=J. Chem. Soc., Trans. | publisher=Royal Society of Chemistry (RSC) | volume=83 | issue=0 | year=1903 | issn=0368-1645 | doi=10.1039/ct9038301021 | pages=1021–1037}}</ref>

